<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Verify Your SendItCourier Email</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; background-color: #f8f9fa; color: #000000;">
<div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.95) 0%, rgba(248,249,250,0.98) 100%); padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(128, 0, 32, 0.2); border: 1px solid rgba(128, 0, 32, 0.3);">
    <h2 style="color: #800020; font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 20px;">Verify Your Email, <%= name %>!</h2>

    <p style="color: #000000; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 15px;">Thank you for registering with <strong><%= appName %></strong>. To complete your email verification, please use the following One-Time Password (OTP):</p>

    <div style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; color: #800020; text-align: center; padding: 15px; background-color: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; border: 1px solid rgba(128, 0, 32, 0.3);">
        <%= otp %>
    </div>

    <p style="color: #000000; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 15px;">This OTP is valid for <strong><%= expiresIn %> minutes</strong>. Please enter it in the verification form on our platform to activate your account.</p>

    <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="#" style="display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #800020 0%, #a00028 100%); color: #ffffff; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin-top: 20px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px; border: 1px solid rgba(128, 0, 32, 0.3); box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(128, 0, 32, 0.15); transition: background 0.3s ease;">Go to Verification</a>
    </div>

    <p style="color: #000000; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 15px;">If you didn’t request this OTP or need assistance, please contact our support team.</p>

    <p style="color: #000000; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5;">Welcome aboard,<br />
        The <%= appName %> Team</p>
</div>

<div style="font-size: 12px; color: #6c757d; margin-top: 30px; text-align: center;">
    © <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> <%= appName %>. All rights reserved.
</div>
</body>
</html>